  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3508820/extras/0e6c5d2bc1dcc0afaa47182d83a281d6.avif?t=1741125207\" width=285 height=285 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After having refused to complete a contract, the assassin Layla is banished by her order to a remote island. There to live out her days in exile.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3508820/extras/2de5aae5843ac7e88306a0aa85db25b9.webp?t=1741125207\" width=89 height=32 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But on the island, strange things are happening. Gods and monsters are stirring, and great events are set in motion. Events which will steer Layla unto a new path, and towards a great destiny.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3508820/extras/2de5aae5843ac7e88306a0aa85db25b9.webp?t=1741125207\" width=89 height=32 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Lantern of Worlds : Layla's Quest</strong> is a short adventure game set in the Lantern of Worlds universe. It is the first game about Layla, her trials and challenges, and her ultimate quest to  exact a great vengeance upon the order that banished her. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3508820/extras/2de5aae5843ac7e88306a0aa85db25b9.webp?t=1741125207\" width=89 height=32 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as the assassin Layla and explore a mysterious island.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight the good fight, against cultist, drowned pirates, water elementals and more!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Increase your fighting skills, and learn magic spells of great power!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meet with strange allies, pirates and wizards, who will aid you in your</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >quest.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unravel the plans of the fire cult and save the island from their dark rituals.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3508820/extras/2de5aae5843ac7e88306a0aa85db25b9.webp?t=1741125207\" width=89 height=32 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lantern of Worlds - Layla's Quest is also part of the free to play game Lantern of Worlds: Storybook. But this is a much improved version.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3508820/extras/b59f7745bbd15405705f3b0ae0a1893c.avif?t=1741125207\" width=296 height=182 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3508820/extras/0e6c5d2bc1dcc0afaa47182d83a281d6.avif?t=1741125207\" width=285 height=285 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After having refused to complete a contract, the assassin Layla is banished by her order to a remote island. There to live out her days in exile.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3508820/extras/2de5aae5843ac7e88306a0aa85db25b9.webp?t=1741125207\" width=89 height=32 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But on the island, strange things are happening. Gods and monsters are stirring, and great events are set in motion. Events which will steer Layla unto a new path, and towards a great destiny.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3508820/extras/2de5aae5843ac7e88306a0aa85db25b9.webp?t=1741125207\" width=89 height=32 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Lantern of Worlds : Layla's Quest</strong> is a short adventure game set in the Lantern of Worlds universe. It is the first game about Layla, her trials and challenges, and her ultimate quest to  exact a great vengeance upon the order that banished her. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3508820/extras/2de5aae5843ac7e88306a0aa85db25b9.webp?t=1741125207\" width=89 height=32 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as the assassin Layla and explore a mysterious island.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight the good fight, against cultist, drowned pirates, water elementals and more!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Increase your fighting skills, and learn magic spells of great power!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meet with strange allies, pirates and wizards, who will aid you in your</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >quest.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unravel the plans of the fire cult and save the island from their dark rituals.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3508820/extras/2de5aae5843ac7e88306a0aa85db25b9.webp?t=1741125207\" width=89 height=32 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lantern of Worlds - Layla's Quest is also part of the free to play game Lantern of Worlds: Storybook. But this is a much improved version.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3508820/extras/b59f7745bbd15405705f3b0ae0a1893c.avif?t=1741125207\" width=296 height=182 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
